T|Purp|0|The approval surface for sl posts. For each post, the sy presents generated imagery and cp variants so the owner just picks and approves — then posts immediately or sends it to the Scheduler. This is one of the main feeders of the Decision Queue (the "ap all three LinkedIn posts" tp items).
