T|The |0|Post context header — e.g. "Instagram post · from 'Claude ran my business'" w/ a "1 of 3 in the experiment" indicator and a "Leonardo generated 8 images" note.
T|The |1|cp variants (A/B) — two text columns prepared by William (copywriting ag):
T|The |2|Variant A and Variant B, each the full ct (e.g. "I gave one business to a team of AI ag for 7 days. Here's exactly what shipped, what broke…"), so the owner can choose the stronger hook. Marked recommended on one.
T|The |3|im grid — 8 generated images from Leonardo in a grid; the owner clicks an im to select it for the post. Includes an "Upload your own im" option.
